Authors = ["UN"]
Name = "☳☶plug - WhiteList"
Description = "Whitelist-based chat filter for Nicotine+.\n\nBehavior:\n  - Blocks public chat from non-whitelisted users\n  - Optionally blocks private messages from non-whitelisted users\n  - Never blocks your own messages\n  - Supports preview logging for blocked messages\n  - Creates periodic JSON backups of the whitelist\n\nCommands:\n  /wla <user>\n    Add user to whitelist\n\n  /wlr <user>\n    Remove user from whitelist\n\n  /wll\n    List whitelisted users\n\n  /wli\n    Import whitelist backup JSON\n\nSettings:\n  enabled\n    Master toggle for whitelist filtering\n\n  whitelist\n    List of allowed usernames\n\n  allow_private_messages\n    ON: private messages from non-whitelisted users are allowed\n    OFF: private messages from non-whitelisted users are blocked\n\n  preview_logging\n    Log blocked messages to the event viewer\n\n  preview_length\n    Number of message characters to include in block logs\n    0 = disable preview text\n\n  blocked_user_log_delay\n    Minimum seconds between block logs per user\n\n  backup_enabled\n    Enable periodic JSON whitelist backups\n\n  backup_interval\n    Minutes between automatic backups\n\nBackup:\n  - Backup file: backup/whitelist_backup.json\n  - Import command: /wli"